               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the second half of the year (fols. 3ra-181rc)&#xD;
I-1) Maggābit (fols. 3ra-35vb)&#xD;
I-2) Miyāzyā (fols. 36ra-60va)&#xD;
I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 61ra-93rb) &#xD;
I-4) Sane (fols. 94ra-122vc)&#xD;
I-5) Ḥamle (fols. 123ra-155ra)&#xD;
I-6) Naḥāse (fols. 156ra-176rb)&#xD;
I-7) Ṗagʷǝmen (fols. 177ra-181ra) &#xD;
- Postscript (commissioner's statement): fol. 181ra&#xD;
- Za-ʾaqrabku māḥleta... “The song I am offering...” (concluding prayer): fol. 181ra-rb&#xD;
The commemorative notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-2.</summary>
